{"id":6417,"date":"2024-01-09T16:46:26","date_gmt":"2020-03-09T11:16:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=6417"},"modified":"2024-02-08T21:57:40","modified_gmt":"2024-02-08T16:27:40","slug":"modern-bed-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-bed-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Want A Dreamy, Soothing Bedroom? Revamp It With These Modern Bed Designs!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Bland bed designs are a thing of the past. Switch over to style with these modern bed ideas<\/em>!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A comfy, soothing bed is like a silent therapist that heals you after a crazy day at work. Snuggle in its warm cocoon, turn over on it without any worry of the world, fall on it like a kid, your bed will never complain. That\u2019s why you should get a bed that lets you thrive at your lowest and peps you up every morning! Unlike the boring and predictable bed designs that all of us think are the norm, how about choosing a fresh, modern style bed for your den?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Got no ideas about modern beds apart from wood, metal and plain colored ones? Fret not, go through our in-depth design curation and easily pick the bed that lovingly whispers your name.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Unique Modern Bed With A Canopy Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for a bed that just stands out? Have a look at this brilliant design then! Handcrafted from wood and posts that encompass the bed, this bed design is straight out of a fairy tale. You can easily customise it with curtains and it gives all the movie feels as well!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011513\/unique-modern-bed-with-canopy-bedroom-design.jpg\" alt=\"Unique modern wooden bed designs with a canopy design for your bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-6418\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011513\/unique-modern-bed-with-canopy-bedroom-design.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011513\/unique-modern-bed-with-canopy-bedroom-design-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011513\/unique-modern-bed-with-canopy-bedroom-design-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011513\/unique-modern-bed-with-canopy-bedroom-design-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Style Bed With A Loft<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Got a compact room for them young teens? Call dibs on this loft bed design then!&nbsp; It is modern, smart and not to mention the latest! You can smartly utilise the area under the loft bed as a study area or you could also arrange one more bed there. Ain\u2019t it looking like an uber-cool bed choice already?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011517\/modern-style-bed-design-with-loft.jpg\" alt=\"Modern style wooden bed designs with a loft to save space for your small bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-6419\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011517\/modern-style-bed-design-with-loft.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011517\/modern-style-bed-design-with-loft-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011517\/modern-style-bed-design-with-loft-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011517\/modern-style-bed-design-with-loft-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Customise your bed and enjoy up to 25 year warranty\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08210059\/customise-your-bed-enjoy-up-to-25-year-warranty.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Adjustable Bed With The Latest Modern Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If your middle name is comfort and luxury like that of ours, look no further. Because an adjustable bed is made just for you! Easy to adjust, streamline as per your day to day needs and mood swings, this bed lets you indulge. This bed is loved as a hot cake because whether you are watching TV, reading or just lazing around, you can adjust it the way you want in a jiffy!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011520\/latest-modern-bedroom-with-adjustable-bed-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Latest modern bedroom with a adjustable modern bed designs to make a luxury look\" class=\"wp-image-6420\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011520\/latest-modern-bedroom-with-adjustable-bed-designs.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011520\/latest-modern-bedroom-with-adjustable-bed-designs-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011520\/latest-modern-bedroom-with-adjustable-bed-designs-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011520\/latest-modern-bedroom-with-adjustable-bed-designs-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Classy Antique Modern Style Bed<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We know that antique designs make you jump with joy and the good news is that they are timeless. So, feel free to fall in love with antique wooden beds, carved with class. This bed design is spacious, designed to perfection and even stunning to look at! Choose this design if you are an art parasite and even otherwise.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011524\/classy-antique-modern-wooden-style-bed-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Modern wooden bed designs with antique wooden beds, carved with class\" class=\"wp-image-6421\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011524\/classy-antique-modern-wooden-style-bed-designs.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011524\/classy-antique-modern-wooden-style-bed-designs-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011524\/classy-antique-modern-wooden-style-bed-designs-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011524\/classy-antique-modern-wooden-style-bed-designs-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bunk Bed To Never Outgrow Your Inner Child<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For kids and adults both, bunk bed feels like a dream come true. It is cozy, adventurous and sparks your child-like imagination all over again. The best part about this bed design is also that it saves more horizontal space. Choose this for sheer joy it lets you feel!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011527\/modern-bunk-bed-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bunk bed designs are perfect for space saving to your kids bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-6422\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011527\/modern-bunk-bed-designs.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011527\/modern-bunk-bed-designs-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011527\/modern-bunk-bed-designs-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011527\/modern-bunk-bed-designs-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Bunk beds are perfect if you want to save space and also want a trendy bedroom!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple And Modern Flat Bed Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A no-frills-attached bed literally and otherwise, a flatbed is perfect for you if you want to keep it simple and comforting in the first place! Despite no substantial support or knick-knacks around it, with the right and comforting mattress, flatbed actually makes for a great choice. Consider it, okay?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011531\/simple-modern-flat-bed-design.jpg\" alt=\"Simple and modern flat bed design with modern bed back wall designs\" class=\"wp-image-6424\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011531\/simple-modern-flat-bed-design.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011531\/simple-modern-flat-bed-design-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011531\/simple-modern-flat-bed-design-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011531\/simple-modern-flat-bed-design-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ultra Modern Bed Design With Slides<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When was the last time you thought about sleeping in a palace, eh? Surprised? Don\u2019t be! Because you can still have a bed with slides by its side or your kid could and feel like a royal! Either way, it is a splendid and spacious bed design. Not to mention super fun to wake up and sweep your way to work or school!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011535\/ultra-modern-bed-design.jpg\" alt=\"Ultra modern bed design with slides for your unique bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-6425\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011535\/ultra-modern-bed-design.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011535\/ultra-modern-bed-design-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011535\/ultra-modern-bed-design-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011535\/ultra-modern-bed-design-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"small space, big style we've got designs for tiny bedroom\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/17141954\/small-space-big-style-got-designs-for-tiny-bedroom.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Metal Design For Modern Bed Decor<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cast iron or crystal metal never gets outdated as a modern decor material. These bed designs have great texture, character and a vintage feel about them! With pastel throws, sheets and pillows, a metal bed can do wonders for your contemporary and chic bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011539\/metal-design-for-modern-bed-decor.jpg\" alt=\"Metal design for modern bed decor to make contemporary and chic bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-6426\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011539\/metal-design-for-modern-bed-decor.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011539\/metal-design-for-modern-bed-decor-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011539\/metal-design-for-modern-bed-decor-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011539\/metal-design-for-modern-bed-decor-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Futon Bed Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Want a bed that is more functional and usable? Futon bed design is just right for you! You use this bed as a snug chair by the day and at night you can easily roll it out to convert into a comfy bed. Utility wise, this bed design is ideal for your cozy abode, telling you!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011543\/futon-modern-bed-design.jpg\" alt=\"Futon modern bed design with a padded chair cum comfy bed for your bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-6427\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011543\/futon-modern-bed-design.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011543\/futon-modern-bed-design-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011543\/futon-modern-bed-design-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011543\/futon-modern-bed-design-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Luxury Bed Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your bed must be luxurious. Nothing more and nothing less. If you second the same then nobody is stopping you from getting a plush, comforting bed all for yourself! For a classy bedroom, settle for nothing but this luxury bed design! It will pep you up at its very first sight.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011546\/new-modern-luxury-bed-design.jpg\" alt=\"New modern luxury bed design with comfort and class for your modern bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-6428\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011546\/new-modern-luxury-bed-design.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011546\/new-modern-luxury-bed-design-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011546\/new-modern-luxury-bed-design-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21011546\/new-modern-luxury-bed-design-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With all of that, make sure to bid a farewell to bad bed designs. Because guess what? Life is too short to not choose a fresh and modern bed design for your kingdom a.k.a bedroom, right? Revamp the same soon with these latest bed designs. For any decor help, feel free to book our consultation!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/choose-bed-for-bedroom\/\">How To Choose A Bed For Your Bedroom<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wall-mounted-murphy-bed-designs\/\">Wall Mounted Murphy Bed Designs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-bedroom-designs\/\">Modern Bedroom Designs For Your Home<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" ac